470
00:26:23,881 --> 00:26:25,670
- Sidecar.
- Pousse-toi.

471
00:26:30,862 --> 00:26:32,034
Je recommence.

472
00:26:36,519 --> 00:26:37,589
Jus d'orange.

473
00:26:38,138 --> 00:26:39,399
Tu regardes ?

474
00:26:42,284 --> 00:26:43,284
Quoi ?

475
00:26:44,635 --> 00:26:46,877
